<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="371" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,764,1308,1574]" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">
This species was previously recorded from Liberian 
<collectingRegion box="[263,343,1342,1368]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">Nimba</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="HILL, J. E." box="[363,491,1342,1368]" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" pagination="116 - 120" refId="ref13738" refString="HILL, J. E. 1982. Records of bats from Mount Nimba, Liberia. Mammalia, 46: 116 - 120." type="journal article" year="1982">Hill, 1982</bibRefCitation>
; Wolton 
<emphasis box="[605,661,1342,1368]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">et al</emphasis>
., 1982). During this study, it was recorded on the Liberian side from 
<quantity box="[280,359,1411,1437]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" unit="m" value="500.0">
<elevation box="[280,359,1411,1437]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" unit="m" value="500.0">500 m</elevation>
</quantity>
to 
<elevation box="[406,574,1411,1437]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" unit="m" value="1000.0">
<quantity box="[406,507,1411,1437]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" unit="m" value="1000.0">1,000 m</quantity>
a.s.l.
</elevation>
in a variety of forested and disturbed habitats. 
<collectingCounty box="[527,545,1445,1471]" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">It</collectingCounty>
was also recorded roosting in old mine adits on 
<collectingMunicipality box="[528,661,1479,1505]" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">Mt Gangra</collectingMunicipality>
and 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03BD87F43F7D6D48FF14FB4FFF0EF9E7:8ECB60393F7D6D48FD37FA5FFEC6F9C2" county="It" municipality="Mt Gangra" name="Mt Yuelliton" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" stateProvince="Nimba">Mt Yuelliton</location>
, adjacent to 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03BD87F43F7D6D48FF14FB4FFF0EF9E7:8ECB60393F7D6D48FE43FA71FE0FF9C2" box="[429,463,1513,1539]" county="It" municipality="Mt Gangra" name="Mt" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" stateProvince="Nimba">Mt</location>
<collectingRegion box="[477,557,1513,1539]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="12" pageNumber="371">Nimba</collectingRegion>
on the 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03BD87F43F7D6D48FF14FB4FFF0EF9E7:8ECB60393F7D6D48FD76FA71FD3BF9C2" box="[664,763,1513,1539]" county="It" municipality="Mt Gangra" name="Liberian" pageId="12" pageNumber="371" stateProvince="Nimba">Liberian</location>
side.
</paragraph>
